OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with patchy cloud,
OL,6,Fespecially through the morning, but
OL,7,Falso sunny spells which will become
OL,8,Fprolonged later. Highest temperatures
OL,9,Finland, breezy and rather cool along
OL,10,Fthe coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry and settled, a band of
OL,13,Fcloud moving southwards overnight and
OL,14,Fclearing the region by the morning.
OL,15,FWinds becoming light and variable.
OL,16,FFeeling cooler overnight.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FA dry and sunny start,
OL,19,Fbecoming cloudy during the afternoon,
OL,20,Fbefore skies clear again overnight.
OL,21,FWinds becoming light and variable.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
