OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FStaying predominantly dry, but with a
OL,7,Fsmall chance of isolated showers on
OL,8,FThursday. Winds light northerly.
OL,9,FTemperatures generally average or
OL,10,Fslightly above.
